Package: mdbackup
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, mariadb-client | mysql-client, gzip, bzip2, xz-utils, gnupg
Recommends: mariadb-server | mysql-server
Description: Comprehensive MariaDB/MySQL backup solution
 MariaDBAutobackup provides an automated backup and recovery solution
 for MariaDB/MySQL databases with the following features:
 .
 * Full, differential, and incremental backups
 * Table-specific backups
 * Backup integrity verification with checksums
 * Configurable compression (gzip, bzip2, xz)
 * Encryption with GPG
 * Remote backups (NFS, rsync, Cloud storage)
 * Pre- and post-backup hooks
 * Automatic cleanup of old backups
 * Progress display
 * Comprehensive prerequisite checking